information: Vimex GmbH is a globally active trading company with headquarters in Bad Neuenahr Ahrweiler, Rheinland-Pfalz. Vimex GmbH was founded in 2014 by Hendrik Voigt. Hendrik has been successfully working in this industry for more than 20 years. He has forged excellent contacts and acquired first-class knowledge of the products and the market. We deal in import and export of beef and pork, as well as of common poultry meat. The main sales markets include Eastern Europe, Asia, the Russian Federation, the Middle East and Africa. We see ourselves as an ideal partner for domestic slaughterhouses and meat-cutting plants as well as for foreign meat processors and importers.
